title: The Very Best Of Classic Freestyle
description:
Ok - HERE are my all time favorite freestyle hits from mostly the 80&#039;s and early 90&#039;s when freestyle was a BIG BIG sound... of course this is limited to what is currently on my hard drive, but I chose the ones that bring back the best memories for me.  I am into probably more of a New York freestyle sound - a harder more fierce sound.

I would list them all here, but all the details are in the "details".

Company B, Cover Girls, Coro, Expose, George Lamond, Sweet Sensation, TKA, Stevie B., Will To Power - just to name a few of the artists here.  Also a select few that never made it real big, but have that sound we all know and love :)

I hope you all will enjoy and reseed as appropriate!
